                    <span>I, as an Harley Davidson enthusiast from Istanbul Chapter in Turkey, found Ron Ayres book very inspiring.After having read the book, I realized that, the book leaves the reader bursting with desire to hit the road anytime, anywhere... It is a wonderful book and I already recommended it to all of my HOG friends.</span>
                  
              
